### Outiiil ###

1- Introduction

Outiiil is a web extension to improve the quality of online game fourmizzz.fr.
This source of this extension is available on github, see : https://github.com/Hraesvelg/Outiiil for more info.

2 - Compile source.

To create a production version, you will need all library minimized :

- Jquery 3.1 : https://jquery.com/
- JqueryUI 1.12 : http://jqueryui.com/ he is customize for Firefox ! replace windows.Globalize with Gloabalie !

- globalize.js 0.1.1 : https://github.com/jquery/globalize
- globalize.culture.fr.js 

- fixedheadertable_1.3.js : http://www.fixedheadertable.com/
- numeral_1.5.3.js : http://numeraljs.com/
- lodash_4.13.1.js : https://lodash.com/
- tablesorter_2.0.js : http://tablesorter.com/docs/
- highcharts_4.1.9.js : http://www.highcharts.com/
- moment_2.10.6.js : http://momentjs.com/
- moment.locale.js

first step : to work correctly copy de source directory !

second step : check the manifest.json, all class in project is minified and regrouped in the main.js
-> the production version contains only lib and a main.js,
-> so you can remove line like "content_scripts/class/...", "content_scripts/boite/...", "content_scripts/page/..."

third step : run ./makefile.sh (pre-resquest to have uglifyjs in your system)
-> the makefile minify all class with uglifyjs and copy the compress code in header of new file main.js.

four step : have fun !
